Generate text response from a prompt.

```javascript
client.setType('text');
const text = await client.generate('Explain AIClient usage');
console.log(text);
```

Generate image from a prompt.

```javascript
client.setType('image');
const blob = await client.generate('A futuristic city skyline');
const url = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
document.querySelector('img').src = url;
```

> Note: `setType('image')` only works correctly after the client instance is created and the type is set explicitly before calling `generate()`.
